#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios/6_2_Hunting_Dwarves.cfg:651
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios/6_2_Hunting_Dwarves.cfg:652
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios/6_2_Hunting_Dwarves.cfg:653
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios/6_2_Hunting_Dwarves.cfg:655
